		<title>How to catch legendary Pokémon (in theory)</title>
		<link>https://rosschurchley.com/blog/2012/how-to-catch-legendary-pokemon-in-theory/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ross]]></dc:creator>
